data.description: Welcome home to this quiet and comfortable 3 bedroom 2.5 bath low maintenance townhome in Lakeland Heights near Island Lake County Park. Entering from your covered porch, you'll step into a spacious floor plan that includes living, dining, kitchen and powder bath on the main floor. A lovely glass door from the kitchen leads to your own private back patio. Upstairs you'll find all three bedrooms, including the primary and primary bath, plus the laundry! This home features a newly updated kitchen, updated baths, new gas furnace and new luxury vinyl laminate floors. You'll even get to park protected from the winter weather in the oversized one car garage. And, you'll spend your winter nights snuggled next to the cozy on-demand gas fireplace.
